@startuml Admin_Account_Management
title Use Case Diagram: Admin Account Management (UC-A4)

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white

left to right direction

actor "Super Admin" as SuperAdmin #FF6B6B

rectangle "Admin Account Management System" {
  usecase "UCA04-1\nView Admin List" as UC1 #E0F0FF
  usecase "UCA04-2\nCreate Admin Account" as UC2 #FFE4B5
  usecase "UCA04-3\nAssign Permissions" as UC3 #FFB6C1
  usecase "UCA04-4\nDelete Admin Account" as UC4 #E0F0FF
}

SuperAdmin --> UC1
SuperAdmin --> UC2
SuperAdmin --> UC3
SuperAdmin --> UC4

' Relationships
UC2 ..> UC1 : <<include>>
UC3 ..> UC1 : <<include>>
UC4 ..> UC1 : <<include>>

note right of UC1
  View all admin accounts
  Filter by role/status
  View activity logs
end note

note right of UC2
  Create pending account
  Send activation email
  Batch import from CSV
end note

note right of UC3
  **HIGH PRIORITY**
  RBAC/ABAC implementation
  Least privilege principle
  Role templates
  Effective permissions view
  Full audit trail
end note

note right of UC4
  Require confirmation
  Prevent last super admin deletion
  Archive instead of delete
  Audit trail
end note

@enduml




